spells.description:
Equip: Carefully balance the Egg's incubation. While stationary, gain 138 Strength every 1 sec, up to 30 times. Diminishes while moving. While moving, gain 139 of your highest secondary stat every 1 sec, up to 30 times. Diminishes while stationary. 

Additional stacks above 20 grant 60% reduced benefit.
Use: Suspend the Egg's incubation state for 20 sec. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Your attacks have a chance to call to the pact, exploding for 182,096 Shadow damage split between nearby enemies and increasing your Haste by 767 for 10 sec.

Your death breaks the pact, causing a violent explosion.

Equip: Taking damage greater than 25% of your health grants you 2,213 Avoidance and increases healing taken by 10% for 10 sec. This effect may only occur every 90 sec.

Falling damage reduced.
